      "description": "Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you glide through the hills in this automotive masterpiece. Every curve of its hand-finished bodywork captures the light like a polished jewel, whispering tales of a golden era of driving. The interior is a sanctuary of fine leather and polished wood, smelling of heritage and adventure. This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule, a pristine companion waiting to ignite your passion for the open road. To drive it is to command the very spirit of elegance.",
      "price": 46800.0,
